            review: "Absent instructors.  Material covered is OK; lectures are not worth watching. Just read the book.\nProject 1 was made unnecessarily hard for many students by enabling sorting. That didn't add to the learning for students.\nHead TA Chris is very unprofessional on slack; mocking students for asking questions.",
